### vNext Runtime API — {{workflowKey}}
### REST Client (.http) — for manual exploration. The xUnit integration tests are CI's source of truth.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4201
@apiVersion = 1
@domain = {{domain}}
@workflowKey = {{workflowKey}}

### Start a new instance
# @name start
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/{{domain}}/workflows/{{workflowKey}}/instances/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  /* Initial payload — match the workflow's master schema required fields */
}

###
@instanceId = {{start.response.body.$.id}}

### Get current state (long-poll for view + data)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/{{domain}}/workflows/{{workflowKey}}/instances/{{instanceId}}/functions/state

### Execute a manual transition
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/{{domain}}/workflows/{{workflowKey}}/instances/{{instanceId}}/transitions/{transition-key}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  /* Transition payload — match the transition's input schema */
}

### Call a function on this instance
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/{{domain}}/workflows/{{workflowKey}}/instances/{{instanceId}}/functions/{function-key}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Retry a failed transition
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/{{domain}}/workflows/{{workflowKey}}/instances/{{instanceId}}/retry

### Query instances (list)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/{{domain}}/workflows/{{workflowKey}}/instances?state={state-key}

### List all instances
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/{{domain}}/workflows/{{workflowKey}}/instances
